title: The Hunter ( Free PC Hunting Game )
description:
For users having trouble to download the game using the Emote Launcher.

Copy the 2009012801 folder to C:Program FilesEmotehunter and overwrite.

Then start the game from the official website and it should install the game.

If it gives an error, close the launcher.exe process from the Task Manager




For people who do not know: You need to register on www.thehunter.com and download the launcher. Then download this torrent and follow the above instructions.
